		<div class="data-note">
			<h2>Data Used In Example Graph</h2>
			<p>The data in our sandbox is from a dolphin social network. It describes an undirected social network of frequent associations between 62 dolphins in a community living off Doubtful Sound, New Zealand. D. Lusseau, K. Schneider, O. J. Boisseau, P. Haase, E. Slooten, and S. M. Dawson, Behavioral Ecology and Sociobiology 54, 396-405 (2003).</p>
			<h3>Things To Watch For</h3>
			<p>As you select different layouts watch how some display popularity, hierarchy and clustering of the dolphin community.</p>
